             were indicted for that <rs id="t17770514-6-off25" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17770514-6-off25" type="offenceCategory" value="violentTheft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17770514-6-off25" type="offenceSubcategory" value="highwayRobbery"></interp>
