                  , <rs id="t17770514-6-viclabel31" type="occupation">spinster</rs>
                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t17770514-6-victim88 t17770514-6-viclabel31"></join>, did make an assault, putting her in corporal fear and danger of her life, and stealing from her person a silk purse, value 2 d. a half guinea and 6 d. in money numbered, the property of the said Ann
            </rs>, <rs id="t17770514-6-cd32" type="crimeDate">April 21st</rs>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17770514-6-off25 t17770514-6-cd32"></join>
                  <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17770514-6-off30 t17770514-6-cd32"></join>
