                     <interp inst="t17770514-6-person92" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
             sworn.</p>
               <p>I know neither of the prisoners.</p>
               <p>HARRIS <rs id="t17770514-6-verdict37" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17770514-6-verdict37" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. <rs id="t17770514-6-punish38" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17770514-6-punish38" type="punishmentCategory" value="death"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17770514-6-defend76 t17770514-6-punish38"></join>
               Death
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>LUCAS <rs id="t17770514-6-verdict39" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17770514-6-verdict39" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
               NOT GUILTY
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Tried by the First Middlesex Jury before Mr. Justice ASTON.</p>
            </div1>
